text.tspan: Forward-thinking marketing professional with a proven background in
finance and administration, supporting clients with cost-effective marketing
campaigns. Develops collateral, executes plans and adjusts strategies to keep
initiatives on-target and achieve target results. Well-organized and diligent
with solid follow-through and unwavering commitment to client goals.
Generate monthly performance metrics and analytical reports, reviewing
and communicating marketing campaign effectiveness to clients.
Oversee marketing for product launches, including public relations,
direct mail pieces, sales training and e-mail campaigns.
Maximize branding initiatives by preparing more than 50 marketing
packages and advertising collateral to secure prospects and increase sales
Prepared monthly and year-end closing statements, financial documents
Managed team of three financial professionals, coaching each employee
Monitored all company costs and presented budget forecasts each
Drafted meeting agendas, supplied advance materials and executed
follow-up for meetings and team conferences.
Updated financial, customer and business records with accurate
information each day, preventing data loss and keeping files current.
Organized over 100 files, developed spreadsheets, faxed reports and
scanned documents to bolster organizational workflow each day.
